text.tspan: Step 1: Convert each task to minutes
Step 3: Get task WEIGHT by dividing common total (1000) by total time of task (600 for ML) plus
ideal chunk (60 for ML) or w = common_total / (task_total + ideal_chunk)
Step 4: Get starting health by using formula 5b
Step 5a: Add ideal chunk MINUTES of task to queue (highest HEALTH first, priority breaks ties)
5b: Use formula to subtract from HP -- 1000 - (60 * 1.67) or h - (c * w)
Step 6a: Add proportional amount of rest time after each task with -- 60 / 2070 * 1080
6b: Use 5b formula to subtract from rest time HP
Step 7: Check Progress each week and take money away if not complete. Give money back if did well
